Sentencas: In this paper, an interconnecting ceramic for solid oxide fuel cells was developed, based on the modification from La0.7Ca0.3CrO3-delta by addition Of Ce0.8SM0.2O1.
Titulo: Novel composite interconnecting ceramics La0.7Ca0.3CrO3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 for solid oxide fuel cells
Novel composite interconnecting ceramics La0.7Ca0.3CrO3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: It is found that addition of small amount Ceo(8)SM(0.2)O(1.9) into La0.7Ca0.3CrO3-delta dramatically increased the electrical conductivity.
Titulo: Novel composite interconnecting ceramics La0.7Ca0.3CrO3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: For the best system, La0.7Ca0.3Cr0-delta,3 + 5 wt.% Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9, the electrical conductivity reached 687.8 S cm(-1) at 800 degrees C in air.
Titulo: Novel composite interconnecting ceramics La0.7Ca0.3CrO3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: In H-2 at 800 degrees C, the specimen with 3 wt.% Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 had the maximal electrical conductivity of 7.1 S cm-1.
Titulo: Novel composite interconnecting ceramics La0.7Ca0.3CrO3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: With the increase of Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 content the relative density increased, reaching 98.7% when the Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 content was 10 wt.%.
Titulo: Novel composite interconnecting ceramics La0.7Ca0.3CrO3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The average coefficient of thermal expansion at 30-100 degrees C in air increased with Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 content, ranging from 11.12 x 10(-6) to 12.46 x 10-6 K-1.
Titulo: Novel composite interconnecting ceramics La0.7Ca0.3CrO3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The oxygen permeation measurement illustrated a negligible oxygen ionic conduction, indicating it is still an electronically conducting ceramic.
Titulo: Novel composite interconnecting ceramics La0.7Ca0.3CrO3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Therefore, this material system will be a very promising interconnect for solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Novel composite interconnecting ceramics La0.7Ca0.3CrO3-δ/Ce0.8Sm0.2O1.9 for solid oxide fuel cells
